      "$description": "Neutral grayscale CONTENT ladder — text, borders, tints. 0=pure-white end-cap; 100=darkest → 1000=lightest (Geist convention). Rebuilt 2026-06-17 (APCA Variant A — monotonic, uniform Lc step ≈8–12). The very-dark app-background tiers (#0F0F0F…#2F2F2F) moved to the separate `surface` group — they sit below this ladder's darkest step (100=#1b1b1b) and anchor the Klyp dark theme."
    },
    "surface": {
      "$description": "Dark neutral SURFACE anchors — the app background hierarchy (FIXES-COLOR §2.1, anchor app-bg #0F0F0F). Kept separate from the neutral content ladder because these very-dark tiers (#0F0F0F…#2F2F2F) sit below the ladder's darkest step (100=#1b1b1b) and must stay fixed to anchor the Klyp dark theme. Consumed by semantic bg.* tokens. Added 2026-06-17.",
      "root": {
        "type": "color",
        "value": "#0f0f0f",
        "description": "⭐ Page background (was neutral.950)."
      },
      "canvas": {
        "type": "color",
        "value": "#121212",
        "description": "Editor canvas — between root and base (was neutral.925)."
      },
      "base": {
        "type": "color",
        "value": "#141414",
        "description": "⭐ Cards / elevated opaque surfaces (was neutral.900)."
      },
      "panel": {
        "type": "color",
        "value": "#181818",
        "description": "Floating-chrome surface — sidebar, composer, right-bar + similar framing panels. Subtle lift above base (#141414): sits at the perceptual midpoint base↔elevated (OKLCH L≈0.209, vs base 0.191 / elevated 0.222), so it softens the base→raised step on panels that frame the workspace rather than sit in it. Added 2026-06-29 (Val)."
      },
      "elevated": {
        "type": "color",
        "value": "#1b1b1b",
        "description": "Intermediate dark surface — one step above base, below raised. Nested low-emphasis cards inside base, list rows; hover target for flat base surfaces. Fills the #141414→#222222 gap (MD3 surface-container-low / Radix gray-2 / Geist gray-200 band; coincides with neutral.100). Added 2026-06-28."
      },
      "raised": {
        "type": "color",
        "value": "#222222",
        "description": "⭐ Buttons / solid chips (was neutral.800)."
      },
      "hover": {
        "type": "color",
        "value": "#2f2f2f",
        "description": "⭐ Hover lift on raised surfaces; also canvas handle selected (was neutral.700 / .775)."
      }
    },
